- **Card Spanning:**
  Use spans to create visual hierarchy (Hero vs. Utility).
  - **Hero:** `col-span-2 row-span-2` (Main focus)
  - **Tall:** `row-span-2` (Lists/Feeds)
  - **Standard:** `col-span-1` (Metrics/Actions)

- **Fluid Typography:**
